    <p class="info"><strong>Class Methods and Class Variables</strong><br>
    If we want every instance of the class Dog to share the same methods or attributes, we must make their scope be the entire class and not just an instance. The syntax for creating <mark><strong>class variables</strong></mark> is @@ and for <mark><strong>class methods</strong></mark> is is self. 
